==Notes==
*{{note label|Note1|nb|nb}}Early in his career, his name was often reported as Zersenay ''Tadesse'', with the letter "s" appearing twice in the surname. The athlete has since clarified that this is incorrect and it is correctly spelt with a single "s" in the surname.<ref name=Focus/>

